ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Astro 525 is an attempt to communicate the most basic statistical tools that we need for our research. In its current form, I would not recommend it to another student, due to its lack of structure.
It would be more useful to students if we have a project or two related to some applications.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: There were a few bits of statistics that I could apply to my work. However, for the most part, the course only covered material I already knew, or material which was never solidified by problem sets.
I picked up some statistics key words which might be helpful.
